== 影響 ==
為慶祝遊戲發行，任天堂在2017年4月把數名本作角色引進手機遊戲《火焰之紋章 英雄》並作可玩角色登場<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2017/04/12/fire-emblem-echoes-characters-coming-to-fe-heroes |title = Fire Emblem Echoes Characters Coming to FE Heroes |last = Osborn |first = Alex |date = 2017-04-13 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2022-03-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112010902/https://www.ign.com/articles/2017/04/12/fire-emblem-echoes-characters-coming-to-fe-heroes |archivedate = 2020-11-12}}</ref>。同年9月，[[光榮特庫摩|光榮特庫摩]]在[[東京電玩展|東京電玩展]]上釋出[[砍殺遊戲|砍殺遊戲]]《[[聖火降魔錄無雙|聖火降魔錄無雙]]》的宣傳影片，本作女主角賽莉卡會以可玩角色身份登場<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=152840 |title = 【TGS 17】《聖火降魔錄無雙》最新宣傳影片「賽莉卡」參戰影像公開 |date = 2017-09-21 |publisher = 巴哈姆特電玩資訊站 |language = zh-tw |accessdate = 2022-03-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210625072156/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=152840 |archivedate = 2021-06-25}}</ref>。玩家亦可以在2018年推出的跨界格鬥遊戲《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥_特別版|任天堂明星大亂鬥 特別版]]》內收集阿雷武、賽莉卡以及飛馬騎士三人組的命魂插圖<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://gamingbolt.com/super-smash-bros-ultimates-next-spirit-board-event-is-a-fire-emblem-fest |title = Super Smash Bros. Ultimate’s Next Spirit Board Event Is A Fire Emblem Fest |last = Parijat |first = Shubhankar |date = 2018-12-19 |publisher = GamingBolt |language = en |accessdate = 2022-03-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220319104702/https://gamingbolt.com/super-smash-bros-ultimates-next-spirit-board-event-is-a-fire-emblem-fest |archivedate = 2022-03-19}}</ref>。遊戲首次採用的兩個新機制（戰技和時間回溯功能）亦在下一部系列主要作品《[[火焰之纹章_风花雪月|火焰之纹章 风花雪月]]》內繼續應用<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.polygon.com/platform/amp/e3/2019/6/12/18662999/fire-emblem-three-houses-divine-pulse-time-travel-turnwheel-revive-e3-2019-nintendo |title = Fire Emblem: Three Houses lets you time travel to fix your dumb mistakes |last = Frushtick |first = Russ |date = 2019-06-12 |publisher = Polygon |language = en |accessdate = 2022-03-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190613174342/https://www.polygon.com/platform/amp/e3/2019/6/12/18662999/fire-emblem-three-houses-divine-pulse-time-travel-turnwheel-revive-e3-2019-nintendo |archivedate = 2019-06-13}}</ref>。此外，玩家可以在《風花雪月》內掃瞄阿雷武和賽莉卡的Amiibo，並在支線任務中解鎖本作的配樂<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.vg247.com/fire-emblem-three-houses-amiibo-unlocks-gazebo |title = Fire Emblem Three Houses amiibo unlocks: what every amiibo does at the gazebo |last = Donaldson |first = Alex |date = 2019-08-09 |publisher = VG247 |language = en |accessdate = 2022-03-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110161116/https://www.vg247.com/fire-emblem-three-houses-amiibo-unlocks-gazebo |archivedate = 2022-01-10}}</ref>。

